data.description: This is a move-in ready, 3 bedroom/2 bath nicely laid-out home in the convenient Legends West subdivision.   Open and spacious kitchen, dining, and living area arrangement offers a very livable floorplan with two living areas, including a fireplace in the family room.  New interior carpet and paint with tasteful, neutral color scheme.  Newly painted exterior stucco and trim.  New stainless kitchen appliances.  New water heater.  Refrigerated air-conditioning. Backyard is a blank canvas perfect for your own dream landscaping design.  Great location on west side of town--close to highway access, schools and shopping.  Hurry, don't miss this one!
